                    <div class="tip-content">
                        <h4>Avoid Common Words</h4>
                        <p>Don't use dictionary words, names, or personal information</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tip-item">
                    <span class="tip-icon">ğŸ”„</span>
                    <div class="tip-content">
                        <h4>Update Regularly</h4>
